{"work":"KJV + Strong's","code":"Nah","book":"Nahum","chapterCount":3,"chapters":[{"number":1,"verses":[{"id":"Nah|1|1","reference":"Nahum 1:1","number":1,"text":"The burden of Nineveh. The book of the vision of Nahum the Elkoshite.","strongs":[{"label":"The burden","strongsId":"H4853"},{"label":"of Nineveh","strongsId":"H5210"},{"label":"The book","strongsId":"H5612"},{"label":"of the vision","strongsId":"H2377"},{"label":"of Nahum","strongsId":"H5151"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|2","reference":"Nahum 1:2","number":2,"text":"God <em>is</em> jealous, and the LORD revengeth; the LORD revengeth, and <em>is</em> furious; the LORD will take vengeance on his adversaries, and he reserveth <em>wrath</em> for his enemies.","strongs":[{"label":"God","strongsId":"H410"},{"label":"em>is</em> jealous","strongsId":"H7072"},{"label":"and the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"revengeth","strongsId":"H5358"},{"label":"the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"revengeth","strongsId":"H5358"},{"label":"and <em>is</em> furious","strongsId":"H1167"},{"label":"and <em>is</em> furious","strongsId":"H2534"},{"label":"the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"will take vengeance","strongsId":"H5358"},{"label":"on his adversaries","strongsId":"H6862"},{"label":"and he reserveth","strongsId":"H5201"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|3","reference":"Nahum 1:3","number":3,"text":"The LORD <em>is</em> slow to anger, and great in power, and will not at all acquit <em>the wicked</em>: the LORD hath his way in the whirlwind and in the storm, and the clouds <em>are</em> the dust of his feet.","strongs":[{"label":"The LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"em>is</em> slow","strongsId":"H750"},{"label":"to anger","strongsId":"H639"},{"label":"and great","strongsId":"H1419"},{"label":"in power","strongsId":"H3581"},{"label":"and will not at all","strongsId":"H5352"},{"label":"acquit","strongsId":"H5352"},{"label":"em>the wicked</em>: the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"hath his way","strongsId":"H1870"},{"label":"in the whirlwind","strongsId":"H5492"},{"label":"and in the storm","strongsId":"H8183"},{"label":"and the clouds","strongsId":"H6051"},{"label":"em>are</em> the dust","strongsId":"H80"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|4","reference":"Nahum 1:4","number":4,"text":"He rebuketh the sea, and maketh it dry, and drieth up all the rivers: Bashan languisheth, and Carmel, and the flower of Lebanon languisheth.","strongs":[{"label":"He rebuketh","strongsId":"H1605"},{"label":"the sea","strongsId":"H3220"},{"label":"and maketh it dry","strongsId":"H2717"},{"label":"and drieth up","strongsId":"H3001"},{"label":"all the rivers","strongsId":"H5104"},{"label":"Bashan","strongsId":"H1316"},{"label":"languisheth","strongsId":"H535"},{"label":"and Carmel","strongsId":"H3760"},{"label":"and the flower","strongsId":"H6525"},{"label":"of Lebanon","strongsId":"H3844"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|5","reference":"Nahum 1:5","number":5,"text":"The mountains quake at him, and the hills melt, and the earth is burned at his presence, yea, the world, and all that dwell","strongs":[{"label":"The mountains","strongsId":"H2022"},{"label":"quake","strongsId":"H7493"},{"label":"at him, and the hills","strongsId":"H1389"},{"label":"melt","strongsId":"H4127"},{"label":"and the earth","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"is burned","strongsId":"H5375"},{"label":"at his presence","strongsId":"H6440"},{"label":"yea, the world","strongsId":"H8398"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|6","reference":"Nahum 1:6","number":6,"text":"Who can stand before his indignation? and who can abide in the fierceness of his anger? his fury is poured out like fire, and the rocks are thrown down","strongs":[{"label":"Who can stand","strongsId":"H5975"},{"label":"before","strongsId":"H6440"},{"label":"his indignation","strongsId":"H2195"},{"label":"and who can abide","strongsId":"H6965"},{"label":"in the fierceness","strongsId":"H2740"},{"label":"of his anger","strongsId":"H639"},{"label":"his fury","strongsId":"H2534"},{"label":"is poured out","strongsId":"H5413"},{"label":"like fire","strongsId":"H784"},{"label":"and the rocks","strongsId":"H6697"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|7","reference":"Nahum 1:7","number":7,"text":"The LORD <em>is</em> good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust","strongs":[{"label":"The LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"em>is</em> good","strongsId":"H2896"},{"label":"a strong hold","strongsId":"H4581"},{"label":"in the day","strongsId":"H3117"},{"label":"of trouble","strongsId":"H6869"},{"label":"and he knoweth","strongsId":"H3045"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|8","reference":"Nahum 1:8","number":8,"text":"But with an overrunning flood he will make an utter end of the place thereof, and darkness shall pursue his enemies.","strongs":[{"label":"But with an overrunning","strongsId":"H5674"},{"label":"flood","strongsId":"H7858"},{"label":"he will make","strongsId":"H6213"},{"label":"an utter end","strongsId":"H3617"},{"label":"of the place","strongsId":"H4725"},{"label":"thereof, and darkness","strongsId":"H2822"},{"label":"shall pursue","strongsId":"H7291"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|9","reference":"Nahum 1:9","number":9,"text":"What do ye imagine against the LORD? he will make an utter end: affliction shall not rise up the second time.","strongs":[{"label":"What do ye imagine","strongsId":"H2803"},{"label":"against the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"he will make","strongsId":"H6213"},{"label":"an utter end","strongsId":"H3617"},{"label":"affliction","strongsId":"H6869"},{"label":"shall not rise up","strongsId":"H6965"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|10","reference":"Nahum 1:10","number":10,"text":"For while <em>they be</em> folden together <em>as</em> thorns, and while they are drunken <em>as</em> drunkards, they shall be devoured as stubble fully dry.","strongs":[{"label":"For while <em>they be</em> folden together","strongsId":"H5440"},{"label":"em>as</em> thorns","strongsId":"H5518"},{"label":"and while they are drunken","strongsId":"H5433"},{"label":"em>as</em> drunkards","strongsId":"H5435"},{"label":"they shall be devoured","strongsId":"H398"},{"label":"as stubble","strongsId":"H7179"},{"label":"fully","strongsId":"H4392"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|11","reference":"Nahum 1:11","number":11,"text":"There is <em>one</em> come out of thee, that imagineth evil against the LORD, a wicked counsellor.","strongs":[{"label":"There is <em>one</em> come out","strongsId":"H3318"},{"label":"of thee, that imagineth","strongsId":"H2803"},{"label":"evil","strongsId":"H7451"},{"label":"against the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"a wicked","strongsId":"H1100"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|12","reference":"Nahum 1:12","number":12,"text":"Thus saith the LORD; Though <em>they be</em> quiet, and likewise many, yet thus shall they be cut down, when he shall pass through. Though I have afflicted thee, I will afflict","strongs":[{"label":"Thus saith","strongsId":"H559"},{"label":"the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"Though <em>they be</em> quiet","strongsId":"H8003"},{"label":"and likewise many","strongsId":"H7227"},{"label":"yet thus shall they be cut down","strongsId":"H1494"},{"label":"when he shall pass through","strongsId":"H5674"},{"label":"Though I have afflicted","strongsId":"H6031"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|13","reference":"Nahum 1:13","number":13,"text":"For now will I break his yoke from off thee, and will burst thy bonds in sunder.","strongs":[{"label":"For now will I break","strongsId":"H7665"},{"label":"his yoke","strongsId":"H4132"},{"label":"from off thee, and will burst","strongsId":"H5423"},{"label":"thy bonds","strongsId":"H4147"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|14","reference":"Nahum 1:14","number":14,"text":"And the LORD hath given a commandment concerning thee, <em>that</em> no more of thy name be sown: out of the house of thy gods will I cut off the graven image and the molten image: I will make thy grave; for thou art vile.","strongs":[{"label":"And the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"hath given a commandment","strongsId":"H6680"},{"label":"concerning thee, <em>that</em> no more of thy name","strongsId":"H8034"},{"label":"be sown","strongsId":"H2232"},{"label":"out of the house","strongsId":"H1004"},{"label":"of thy gods","strongsId":"H430"},{"label":"will I cut off","strongsId":"H3772"},{"label":"the graven image","strongsId":"H6459"},{"label":"and the molten image","strongsId":"H4541"},{"label":"I will make","strongsId":"H7760"},{"label":"thy grave","strongsId":"H6913"}]},{"id":"Nah|1|15","reference":"Nahum 1:15","number":15,"text":"Behold upon the mountains the feet of him that bringeth good tidings, that publisheth peace! O Judah, keep thy solemn feasts, perform thy vows: for the wicked shall no more pass through thee; he is utterly cut off.","strongs":[{"label":"Behold upon the mountains","strongsId":"H2022"},{"label":"the feet","strongsId":"H7272"},{"label":"of him that bringeth good tidings","strongsId":"H1319"},{"label":"that publisheth","strongsId":"H8085"},{"label":"peace","strongsId":"H7965"},{"label":"O Judah","strongsId":"H3063"},{"label":"keep","strongsId":"H2287"},{"label":"thy solemn feasts","strongsId":"H2282"},{"label":"perform","strongsId":"H7999"},{"label":"thy vows","strongsId":"H5088"},{"label":"for the wicked","strongsId":"H1100"},{"label":"shall no more","strongsId":"H3254"},{"label":"pass through","strongsId":"H5674"}]}]},{"number":2,"verses":[{"id":"Nah|2|1","reference":"Nahum 2:1","number":1,"text":"He that dasheth in pieces is come up before thy face: keep the munition, watch the way, make <em>thy</em> loins strong, fortify <em>thy</em> power mightily.","strongs":[{"label":"He that dasheth in pieces","strongsId":"H6327"},{"label":"is come up","strongsId":"H5927"},{"label":"before thy face","strongsId":"H6440"},{"label":"keep","strongsId":"H5341"},{"label":"the munition","strongsId":"H4694"},{"label":"watch","strongsId":"H6822"},{"label":"the way","strongsId":"H1870"},{"label":"make <em>thy</em> loins","strongsId":"H4975"},{"label":"strong","strongsId":"H2388"},{"label":"fortify","strongsId":"H553"},{"label":"em>thy</em> power","strongsId":"H3581"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|2","reference":"Nahum 2:2","number":2,"text":"For the LORD hath turned away the excellency of Jacob, as the excellency of Israel: for the emptiers have emptied them out, and marred their vine branches.","strongs":[{"label":"For the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"hath turned away","strongsId":"H7725"},{"label":"the excellency","strongsId":"H1347"},{"label":"of Jacob","strongsId":"H3290"},{"label":"as the excellency","strongsId":"H1347"},{"label":"of Israel","strongsId":"H3478"},{"label":"for the emptiers","strongsId":"H1238"},{"label":"have emptied them out","strongsId":"H1238"},{"label":"and marred","strongsId":"H7843"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|3","reference":"Nahum 2:3","number":3,"text":"The shield of his mighty men is made red, the valiant men <em>are</em> in scarlet: the chariots <em>shall be</em> with flaming torches in the day of his preparation, and the fir trees shall be terribly shaken.","strongs":[{"label":"The shield","strongsId":"H4043"},{"label":"of his mighty men","strongsId":"H1368"},{"label":"is made red","strongsId":"H119"},{"label":"the valiant","strongsId":"H2428"},{"label":"men","strongsId":"H582"},{"label":"em>are</em> in scarlet","strongsId":"H8529"},{"label":"the chariots","strongsId":"H7393"},{"label":"em>shall be</em> with flaming","strongsId":"H784"},{"label":"torches","strongsId":"H6393"},{"label":"in the day","strongsId":"H3117"},{"label":"of his preparation","strongsId":"H3559"},{"label":"and the fir trees","strongsId":"H1265"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|4","reference":"Nahum 2:4","number":4,"text":"The chariots shall rage in the streets, they shall justle one against another in the broad ways: they shall seem like torches, they shall run like the lightnings.","strongs":[{"label":"The chariots","strongsId":"H7393"},{"label":"shall rage","strongsId":"H1984"},{"label":"in the streets","strongsId":"H2351"},{"label":"they shall justle one against another","strongsId":"H8264"},{"label":"in the broad ways","strongsId":"H7339"},{"label":"they shall seem","strongsId":"H4758"},{"label":"like torches","strongsId":"H3940"},{"label":"they shall run","strongsId":"H7323"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|5","reference":"Nahum 2:5","number":5,"text":"He shall recount his worthies: they shall stumble in their walk; they shall make haste to the wall thereof, and the defence shall be prepared.","strongs":[{"label":"He shall recount","strongsId":"H2142"},{"label":"his worthies","strongsId":"H117"},{"label":"they shall stumble","strongsId":"H3782"},{"label":"in their walk","strongsId":"H1979"},{"label":"they shall make haste","strongsId":"H4116"},{"label":"to the wall","strongsId":"H2346"},{"label":"thereof, and the defence","strongsId":"H5526"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|6","reference":"Nahum 2:6","number":6,"text":"The gates of the rivers shall be opened, and the palace shall be dissolved.","strongs":[{"label":"The gates","strongsId":"H8179"},{"label":"of the rivers","strongsId":"H5104"},{"label":"shall be opened","strongsId":"H6605"},{"label":"and the palace","strongsId":"H1964"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|7","reference":"Nahum 2:7","number":7,"text":"And Huzzab shall be led away captive, she shall be brought up, and her maids shall lead <em>her</em> as with the voice of doves, tabering upon their breasts.","strongs":[{"label":"And Huzzab","strongsId":"H5324"},{"label":"shall be led away captive","strongsId":"H1540"},{"label":"she shall be brought up","strongsId":"H5927"},{"label":"and her maids","strongsId":"H519"},{"label":"shall lead","strongsId":"H5090"},{"label":"em>her</em> as with the voice","strongsId":"H6963"},{"label":"of doves","strongsId":"H3123"},{"label":"tabering","strongsId":"H8608"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|8","reference":"Nahum 2:8","number":8,"text":"But Nineveh <em>is</em> of old like a pool of water: yet they shall flee away. Stand, stand, <em>shall they cry</em>; but none shall look back.","strongs":[{"label":"But Nineveh","strongsId":"H5210"},{"label":"em>is</em> of old","strongsId":"H3117"},{"label":"like a pool","strongsId":"H1295"},{"label":"of water","strongsId":"H4325"},{"label":"yet they shall flee away","strongsId":"H5127"},{"label":"Stand","strongsId":"H5975"},{"label":"stand","strongsId":"H5975"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|9","reference":"Nahum 2:9","number":9,"text":"Take ye the spoil of silver, take the spoil of gold: for <em>there is</em> none end of the store <em>and</em> glory out of all the pleasant furniture.","strongs":[{"label":"Take ye the spoil","strongsId":"H962"},{"label":"of silver","strongsId":"H3701"},{"label":"take the spoil","strongsId":"H962"},{"label":"of gold","strongsId":"H2091"},{"label":"for <em>there is</em> none end","strongsId":"H7097"},{"label":"of the store","strongsId":"H8498"},{"label":"em>and</em> glory","strongsId":"H3519"},{"label":"out of all the pleasant","strongsId":"H2532"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|10","reference":"Nahum 2:10","number":10,"text":"She is empty, and void, and waste: and the heart melteth, and the knees smite together, and much pain <em>is</em> in all loins, and the faces of them all gather blackness.","strongs":[{"label":"She is empty","strongsId":"H950"},{"label":"and void","strongsId":"H4003"},{"label":"and waste","strongsId":"H1110"},{"label":"and the heart","strongsId":"H3820"},{"label":"melteth","strongsId":"H4549"},{"label":"and the knees","strongsId":"H1290"},{"label":"smite together","strongsId":"H6375"},{"label":"and much pain","strongsId":"H2479"},{"label":"em>is</em> in all loins","strongsId":"H4975"},{"label":"and the faces","strongsId":"H6440"},{"label":"of them all gather","strongsId":"H6908"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|11","reference":"Nahum 2:11","number":11,"text":"Where <em>is</em> the dwelling of the lions, and the feedingplace of the young lions, where the lion, <em>even</em> the old lion, walked, <em>and</em> the lion's whelp, and none made <em>them</em> afraid?","strongs":[{"label":"Where <em>is</em> the dwelling","strongsId":"H4583"},{"label":"of the lions","strongsId":"H738"},{"label":"and the feedingplace","strongsId":"H4829"},{"label":"of the young lions","strongsId":"H3715"},{"label":"where the lion","strongsId":"H738"},{"label":"em>even</em> the old lion","strongsId":"H3833"},{"label":"walked","strongsId":"H1980"},{"label":"em>and</em> the lion's","strongsId":"H738"},{"label":"whelp","strongsId":"H1482"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|12","reference":"Nahum 2:12","number":12,"text":"The lion did tear in pieces enough for his whelps, and strangled for his lionesses, and filled his holes with prey, and his dens with ravin.","strongs":[{"label":"The lion","strongsId":"H738"},{"label":"did tear in pieces","strongsId":"H2963"},{"label":"enough","strongsId":"H1767"},{"label":"for his whelps","strongsId":"H1484"},{"label":"and strangled","strongsId":"H2614"},{"label":"for his lionesses","strongsId":"H3833"},{"label":"and filled","strongsId":"H4390"},{"label":"his holes","strongsId":"H2356"},{"label":"with prey","strongsId":"H2964"},{"label":"and his dens","strongsId":"H4585"}]},{"id":"Nah|2|13","reference":"Nahum 2:13","number":13,"text":"Behold, I <em>am</em> against thee, saith the LORD of hosts, and I will burn her chariots in the smoke, and the sword shall devour thy young lions: and I will cut off thy prey from the earth, and the voice of thy messengers shall no more be heard.","strongs":[{"label":"Behold, I <em>am</em> against thee, saith","strongsId":"H5002"},{"label":"the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"of hosts","strongsId":"H6635"},{"label":"and I will burn","strongsId":"H1197"},{"label":"her chariots","strongsId":"H7393"},{"label":"in the smoke","strongsId":"H6227"},{"label":"and the sword","strongsId":"H2719"},{"label":"shall devour","strongsId":"H398"},{"label":"thy young lions","strongsId":"H3715"},{"label":"and I will cut off","strongsId":"H3772"},{"label":"thy prey","strongsId":"H2964"},{"label":"from the earth","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"and the voice","strongsId":"H6963"},{"label":"of thy messengers","strongsId":"H4397"}]}]},{"number":3,"verses":[{"id":"Nah|3|1","reference":"Nahum 3:1","number":1,"text":"Woe to the bloody city! it <em>is</em> all full of lies <em>and</em> robbery; the prey departeth","strongs":[{"label":"Woe","strongsId":"H1945"},{"label":"to the bloody","strongsId":"H1818"},{"label":"city","strongsId":"H5892"},{"label":"it <em>is</em> all full","strongsId":"H4392"},{"label":"of lies","strongsId":"H3585"},{"label":"em>and</em> robbery","strongsId":"H6563"},{"label":"the prey","strongsId":"H2964"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|2","reference":"Nahum 3:2","number":2,"text":"The noise of a whip, and the noise of the rattling of the wheels, and of the pransing horses, and of the jumping chariots.","strongs":[{"label":"The noise","strongsId":"H6963"},{"label":"of a whip","strongsId":"H7752"},{"label":"and the noise","strongsId":"H6963"},{"label":"of the rattling","strongsId":"H7494"},{"label":"of the wheels","strongsId":"H212"},{"label":"and of the pransing","strongsId":"H1725"},{"label":"horses","strongsId":"H5483"},{"label":"and of the jumping","strongsId":"H7540"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|3","reference":"Nahum 3:3","number":3,"text":"The horseman lifteth up both the bright sword and the glittering spear: and <em>there is</em> a multitude of slain, and a great number of carcases; and <em>there is</em> none end of <em>their</em> corpses; they stumble upon their corpses:","strongs":[{"label":"The horseman","strongsId":"H6571"},{"label":"lifteth up","strongsId":"H5927"},{"label":"both the bright","strongsId":"H3851"},{"label":"sword","strongsId":"H2719"},{"label":"and the glittering","strongsId":"H1300"},{"label":"spear","strongsId":"H2595"},{"label":"and <em>there is</em> a multitude","strongsId":"H7230"},{"label":"of slain","strongsId":"H2491"},{"label":"and a great","strongsId":"H3514"},{"label":"number of carcases","strongsId":"H6297"},{"label":"and <em>there is</em> none end","strongsId":"H7097"},{"label":"of <em>their</em> corpses","strongsId":"H1472"},{"label":"they stumble","strongsId":"H3782"},{"label":"they stumble","strongsId":"H3782"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|4","reference":"Nahum 3:4","number":4,"text":"Because of the multitude of the whoredoms of the wellfavoured harlot, the mistress of witchcrafts, that selleth nations through her whoredoms, and families through her witchcrafts.","strongs":[{"label":"Because of the multitude","strongsId":"H7230"},{"label":"of the whoredoms","strongsId":"H2183"},{"label":"of the wellfavoured","strongsId":"H2896"},{"label":"of the wellfavoured","strongsId":"H2580"},{"label":"harlot","strongsId":"H2181"},{"label":"the mistress","strongsId":"H1172"},{"label":"of witchcrafts","strongsId":"H3785"},{"label":"that selleth","strongsId":"H4376"},{"label":"nations","strongsId":"H1471"},{"label":"through her whoredoms","strongsId":"H2183"},{"label":"and families","strongsId":"H4940"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|5","reference":"Nahum 3:5","number":5,"text":"Behold, I <em>am</em> against thee, saith the LORD of hosts; and I will discover thy skirts upon thy face, and I will shew the nations thy nakedness, and the kingdoms thy shame.","strongs":[{"label":"Behold, I <em>am</em> against thee, saith","strongsId":"H5002"},{"label":"the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"of hosts","strongsId":"H6635"},{"label":"and I will discover","strongsId":"H1540"},{"label":"thy skirts","strongsId":"H7757"},{"label":"upon thy face","strongsId":"H6440"},{"label":"and I will shew","strongsId":"H7200"},{"label":"the nations","strongsId":"H1471"},{"label":"thy nakedness","strongsId":"H4626"},{"label":"and the kingdoms","strongsId":"H4467"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|6","reference":"Nahum 3:6","number":6,"text":"And I will cast abominable filth upon thee, and make thee vile, and will set thee as a gazingstock.","strongs":[{"label":"And I will cast","strongsId":"H7993"},{"label":"abominable filth","strongsId":"H8251"},{"label":"upon thee, and make thee vile","strongsId":"H5034"},{"label":"and will set","strongsId":"H7760"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|7","reference":"Nahum 3:7","number":7,"text":"And it shall come to pass, <em>that</em> all they that look upon thee shall flee from thee, and say, Nineveh is laid waste: who will bemoan her? whence shall I seek comforters","strongs":[{"label":"And it shall come to pass, <em>that</em> all they that look","strongsId":"H7200"},{"label":"upon thee shall flee","strongsId":"H5074"},{"label":"from thee, and say","strongsId":"H559"},{"label":"Nineveh","strongsId":"H5210"},{"label":"is laid waste","strongsId":"H7703"},{"label":"who will bemoan","strongsId":"H5110"},{"label":"her? whence","strongsId":"H370"},{"label":"shall I seek","strongsId":"H1245"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|8","reference":"Nahum 3:8","number":8,"text":"Art thou better than populous No, that was situate among the rivers, <em>that had</em> the waters round about it, whose rampart <em>was</em> the sea, <em>and</em> her wall <em>was</em> from the sea?","strongs":[{"label":"Art thou better","strongsId":"H3190"},{"label":"than populous","strongsId":"H527"},{"label":"than populous","strongsId":"H528"},{"label":"No","strongsId":"H4996"},{"label":"that was situate","strongsId":"H3427"},{"label":"among the rivers","strongsId":"H2975"},{"label":"em>that had</em> the waters","strongsId":"H4325"},{"label":"round about","strongsId":"H5439"},{"label":"it, whose rampart","strongsId":"H2426"},{"label":"em>was</em> the sea","strongsId":"H3220"},{"label":"em>and</em> her wall","strongsId":"H2346"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|9","reference":"Nahum 3:9","number":9,"text":"Ethiopia and Egypt <em>were</em> her strength, and <em>it was</em> infinite; Put and Lubim were thy helpers.","strongs":[{"label":"Ethiopia","strongsId":"H3568"},{"label":"and Egypt","strongsId":"H4714"},{"label":"em>were</em> her strength","strongsId":"H6109"},{"label":"and <em>it was</em> infinite","strongsId":"H369"},{"label":"and <em>it was</em> infinite","strongsId":"H7097"},{"label":"Put","strongsId":"H6316"},{"label":"and Lubim","strongsId":"H3864"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|10","reference":"Nahum 3:10","number":10,"text":"Yet <em>was</em> she carried away, she went into captivity: her young children also were dashed in pieces at the top of all the streets: and they cast lots for her honourable men, and all her great men were bound in chains.","strongs":[{"label":"Yet <em>was</em> she carried away","strongsId":"H1473"},{"label":"she went","strongsId":"H1980"},{"label":"into captivity","strongsId":"H7628"},{"label":"her young children","strongsId":"H5768"},{"label":"also were dashed in pieces","strongsId":"H7376"},{"label":"at the top","strongsId":"H7218"},{"label":"of all the streets","strongsId":"H2351"},{"label":"and they cast","strongsId":"H3032"},{"label":"lots","strongsId":"H1486"},{"label":"for her honourable men","strongsId":"H3513"},{"label":"and all her great men","strongsId":"H1419"},{"label":"were bound","strongsId":"H7576"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|11","reference":"Nahum 3:11","number":11,"text":"Thou also shalt be drunken: thou shalt be hid, thou also shalt seek strength because of the enemy.","strongs":[{"label":"Thou also shalt be drunken","strongsId":"H7937"},{"label":"thou shalt be hid","strongsId":"H5956"},{"label":"thou also shalt seek","strongsId":"H1245"},{"label":"strength","strongsId":"H4581"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|12","reference":"Nahum 3:12","number":12,"text":"All thy strong holds <em>shall be like</em> fig trees with the firstripe figs: if they be shaken, they shall even fall into the mouth of the eater.","strongs":[{"label":"All thy strong holds","strongsId":"H4013"},{"label":"em>shall be like</em> fig trees","strongsId":"H8384"},{"label":"with the firstripe figs","strongsId":"H1061"},{"label":"if they be shaken","strongsId":"H5128"},{"label":"they shall even fall","strongsId":"H5307"},{"label":"into the mouth","strongsId":"H6310"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|13","reference":"Nahum 3:13","number":13,"text":"Behold, thy people in the midst of thee <em>are</em> women: the gates of thy land shall be set wide open unto thine enemies: the fire shall devour thy bars.","strongs":[{"label":"Behold, thy people","strongsId":"H5971"},{"label":"in the midst","strongsId":"H7130"},{"label":"of thee <em>are</em> women","strongsId":"H802"},{"label":"the gates","strongsId":"H8179"},{"label":"of thy land","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"shall be set wide","strongsId":"H6605"},{"label":"open","strongsId":"H6605"},{"label":"unto thine enemies","strongsId":"H341"},{"label":"the fire","strongsId":"H784"},{"label":"shall devour","strongsId":"H398"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|14","reference":"Nahum 3:14","number":14,"text":"Draw thee waters for the siege, fortify thy strong holds: go into clay, and tread the morter, make strong the brickkiln.","strongs":[{"label":"Draw","strongsId":"H7579"},{"label":"thee waters","strongsId":"H4325"},{"label":"for the siege","strongsId":"H4692"},{"label":"fortify","strongsId":"H2388"},{"label":"thy strong holds","strongsId":"H4013"},{"label":"go","strongsId":"H935"},{"label":"into clay","strongsId":"H2916"},{"label":"and tread","strongsId":"H7429"},{"label":"the morter","strongsId":"H2563"},{"label":"make strong","strongsId":"H2388"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|15","reference":"Nahum 3:15","number":15,"text":"There shall the fire devour thee; the sword shall cut thee off, it shall eat thee up like the cankerworm: make thyself many as the cankerworm, make thyself many as the locusts.","strongs":[{"label":"There shall the fire","strongsId":"H784"},{"label":"devour","strongsId":"H398"},{"label":"thee; the sword","strongsId":"H2719"},{"label":"shall cut thee off","strongsId":"H3772"},{"label":"it shall eat thee up","strongsId":"H398"},{"label":"like the cankerworm","strongsId":"H3218"},{"label":"make thyself many","strongsId":"H3513"},{"label":"as the cankerworm","strongsId":"H3218"},{"label":"make thyself many","strongsId":"H3513"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|16","reference":"Nahum 3:16","number":16,"text":"Thou hast multiplied thy merchants above the stars of heaven: the cankerworm spoileth, and flieth away.","strongs":[{"label":"Thou hast multiplied","strongsId":"H7235"},{"label":"thy merchants","strongsId":"H7402"},{"label":"above the stars","strongsId":"H3556"},{"label":"of heaven","strongsId":"H8064"},{"label":"the cankerworm","strongsId":"H3218"},{"label":"spoileth","strongsId":"H6584"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|17","reference":"Nahum 3:17","number":17,"text":"Thy crowned <em>are</em> as the locusts, and thy captains as the great grasshoppers, which camp in the hedges in the cold day, <em>but</em> when the sun ariseth they flee away, and their place is not known where","strongs":[{"label":"Thy crowned","strongsId":"H4502"},{"label":"em>are</em> as the locusts","strongsId":"H697"},{"label":"and thy captains","strongsId":"H2951"},{"label":"as the great grasshoppers","strongsId":"H1462"},{"label":"which camp","strongsId":"H2583"},{"label":"in the hedges","strongsId":"H1448"},{"label":"in the cold","strongsId":"H7135"},{"label":"day","strongsId":"H3117"},{"label":"em>but</em> when the sun","strongsId":"H8121"},{"label":"ariseth","strongsId":"H2224"},{"label":"they flee away","strongsId":"H5074"},{"label":"and their place","strongsId":"H4725"},{"label":"is not known","strongsId":"H3045"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|18","reference":"Nahum 3:18","number":18,"text":"Thy shepherds slumber, O king of Assyria: thy nobles shall dwell <em>in the dust</em>: thy people is scattered upon the mountains, and no man gathereth","strongs":[{"label":"Thy shepherds","strongsId":"H7462"},{"label":"slumber","strongsId":"H5123"},{"label":"O king","strongsId":"H4428"},{"label":"of Assyria","strongsId":"H804"},{"label":"thy nobles","strongsId":"H117"},{"label":"shall dwell","strongsId":"H7931"},{"label":"em>in the dust</em>: thy people","strongsId":"H5971"},{"label":"is scattered","strongsId":"H6335"},{"label":"upon the mountains","strongsId":"H2022"}]},{"id":"Nah|3|19","reference":"Nahum 3:19","number":19,"text":"<em>There is</em> no healing of thy bruise; thy wound is grievous: all that hear the bruit of thee shall clap the hands over thee: for upon whom hath not thy wickedness passed continually?","strongs":[{"label":"em>There is</em> no healing","strongsId":"H3545"},{"label":"of thy bruise","strongsId":"H7667"},{"label":"thy wound","strongsId":"H4347"},{"label":"is grievous","strongsId":"H2470"},{"label":"all that hear","strongsId":"H8085"},{"label":"the bruit","strongsId":"H8088"},{"label":"of thee shall clap","strongsId":"H8628"},{"label":"the hands","strongsId":"H3709"},{"label":"over thee: for upon whom hath not thy wickedness","strongsId":"H7451"},{"label":"passed","strongsId":"H5674"}]}]}]}
